<div style="
    max-width: 640px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #D3D3D3;
    margin: 20px auto;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #333;
    background-color: #ffffff;
">
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    ">
        <img src="cid:ethicappLogo" style="max-width: 200px;" alt="Ethicapp Logo" />
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Hello <strong><%= firstName %>,</strong></p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">We are thrilled to inform you that your EthicApp account is now ready for use!</p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        As a member of EthicApp, you’ll have the opportunity to lead meaningful discussions and analyses on ethical cases with your students, fostering critical thinking and insightful conversations. Your guidance will be essential as they navigate complex ethical scenarios and develop their own frameworks for ethical decision-making.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        We're excited to support you as you embark on this journey, and we’re confident EthicApp will become a valuable asset in your teaching toolkit.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        If you need any assistance, our team is here to help. Just reach out, and we’ll be happy to assist you in making the most out of EthicApp.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
        <a href="<%= ethicAppUrl %>" style="
            background-color: #2649EC;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
        ">
            Go to EthicApp
        </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Happy teaching and exploring!</p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Warm regards,</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>The EthicApp Team</strong></p>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
        Welcome to the EthicApp community, where teaching ethics is more impactful than ever.
    </p>
</div>
